DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"No Enemies" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(37473,201)"}              37473,201

                         I don't know whether this is just a glitch
                         caused by incompatability, or maybe a dodgy
                         copy, but if you hit the barrier (with or
                         without the POKE), you will be stuck there
                         and you have to reload the game!

                         Rastan.
